<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1913_01_21_an_FletcherWalterMorley"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> an <persName key="FletcherWalterMorley" role="recipient" full="yes">Walter Morley Fletcher</persName>, 21. 1. 1913</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Original an der Trinity College Library; Kopie im BA.</p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><profileDesc> <creation>Brief geschrieben am 1913_01_21.</creation> </profileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>2007/06: Conversion from Folio Flat File to XML</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="transcript" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"> <p rend="right">21.1.13.</p> <p rend="right">IV. ALLEEGASSE 16.</p> <p rend="right">Wien</p> <p>Dear D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Fletcher,</p> <p rend="indent">My father died yesterday. I will leave Vienna on Saturday 25<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> &amp; shall get to Cambridge either on Sunday night or Monday morning.</p> <p rend="indent">Yours sincerely</p> <p rend="right">Ludwig Wittgenstein</p> </div></body></text></TEI>